# No environment variables are required to build or run this site.
#
# The only process.env reference in the codebase (VERCEL_GIT_COMMIT_SHA) is a
# Vercel System Environment Variable that is no longer consumed anywhere
# (the public build-hash display was removed); it is optional and simply
# resolves to null on any other host, including Hostinger.
#
# The production canonical domain (https://globalkavish.com) is hardcoded in
# src/lib/seo.ts, not sourced from an environment variable.
